      <div class="msgContentFrame">Yeah, it can get pretty annoying. I didn't notice the sp difference, but I don't pay attention that much, will just further annoy me if I do. The other problem I have with it is that other people can just run up and kill the other monsters for you. I know they are trying to help, but when you're just fine, you lose the experience from killing it yourself. Whenever I'm playing with my roommate this is an issue when we aren't doing leves. I can handle multiple monsters, even on my crappy laggy laptop. Guess it doesn't help, no matter what job I play, I'm more geared toward being a tank and doing crowd control.  <br /> <br />I just want to /sigh anytime we get unneeded help from people. Would be nice to claim multiple mobs, within reason. They can then add the call help ability like on FFXI. Then people will be able to get help when needed. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/557565.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
